window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> best-selling author Ava Harrison comes a billionaire romance full of witty banter and a jaw-dropping twist!&nbsp;&nbsp;</b></p> <p>I ran. <br> Escaped the man who wanted to hurt me. <br> I got in my car and drove. <br> No destination. No direction. No help. <br> I hid in the one place I would never be found. <br> Now in New York with no job, I didnâ€™t know what to do. Then I met him. Jaxson Price. <br> The enigmatic devil who wasn't only above the law, but played it like a puppet. <br> He might be the answer to all my problems. <br> Too bad he's asking for something in return for his help.... My heart.</p>"; 
